    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Configuration
    Configuration class to store the configuration details
    ConfigurationRepository
    Repository interface for accessing Configuration data stored in MongoDB.
    Customer
    Customer class to store the customer details
    CustomerController
    Rest controller for customer related operations Provides an endpoint to get all customers
    CustomerRepository
    Repository interface for accessing Customer data stored in MongoDB.
    CustomerService
    Service class for managing customer-related operations during the ticket simulation.
    DefaultConfig
    Component used to initialize the default configuration for the application.
    RealimeTicketingSystemBackendApplication
    Main class to start the Spring Boot application.
    SystemLogger
    SystemLogger class is used to store the logs of the system
    TicketingController
    REST Controller that handles API endpoints for the Real-Time Ticketing System.
    TicketPool
    TicketPool class to manage the tickets in the system.
    TicketService
    Service class for managing ticket-related operations during the ticket simulation.
    TicketStatus
    TicketStatus class is used to store the status of the tickets
    Vendor
    Vendor class to store vendor's ticket release details.
    VendorController
    Rest controller for vendor Provides endpoints for getting all vendors
    VendorRepository
    Repository interface for accessing Vendor data stored in MongoDB.
    VendorService
    Service class for managing vendor-related operations during the ticket simulation.
    WebSocketConnect
    WebSocket configuration for enabling WebSocket message handling and message broker for the application.
    WebSocketCorsConfig
    Cross-origin resource sharing (CORS).
